AI / LLM SDKs (optional, runtime-loaded)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

When AI features are enabled, AuraBoot integrates with third-party LLM
providers via their official SDKs or REST APIs. The provider SDKs and
their respective licenses apply only when the corresponding feature is
enabled and configured by the operator. AuraBoot does not redistribute
provider-specific credentials, model weights, or proprietary content.

================================================================================
Generating a Complete Bill of Materials
================================================================================

For a complete and authoritative dependency list, run:

  Backend:   cd platform && ./gradlew dependencyReport
  Frontend:  cd web-admin && pnpm licenses list

Or use a dedicated tool such as `licensee`, `FOSSA`, `Snyk`, or `cyclonedx`
to produce an SBOM for a given build artifact.
